            <description><![CDATA[【图书馆走进院系在线系列讲座】讲座六 ：ScienceDirect助力科研]]></description>
            <link>https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/04/11/120717</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="true">https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/04/11/120717</guid>
